♪ Don't ♪

696
00:30:03.384 --> 00:30:08.014
♪ Lose yourself ♪

697
00:30:09.682 --> 00:30:13.436
♪ Don't ♪

698
00:30:13.520 --> 00:30:18.733
♪ Lose yourself ♪

699
00:30:19.859 --> 00:30:22.320
♪ Don't ♪

700
00:30:22.403 --> 00:30:25.657
♪ Don't lose yourself ♪

701
00:30:25.740 --> 00:30:30.119
[vocalizing]

702
00:30:31.037 --> 00:30:34.123
[music fades]
